  "remarks": "\nVladimir Nikolayevich KNYAGININ is Vice Governor of Saint Petersburg for the Administration of Saint Petersburg, a public body subordinate to the Government of Russia. As Vice Governor, KNYAGININ is or has been involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia as a Director or equivalent of a Government of Russia-affiliated entity.  \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
